  "original_title": "\u0da2\u0db1\u0db4\u0dad\u0dd2\u0dc0\u0dbb\u0dba\u0dcf\u0d9c\u0dda \u0d89\u0dbd\u0dca\u0dbd\u0dcf \u0d85\u0dc3\u0dca\u0dc0\u0dd2\u0db8\u0dda \u0dbd\u0dd2\u0db4\u0dd2\u0dba \u0dad\u0dc0\u0db8\u0dad\u0dca \u0db1\u0dd1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The resignation letter of the President is not yet available",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "It is reported that the letter regarding the resignation of President Gotabaya Rajapaksa has not yet been forwarded to Speaker Mahinda Yapa Abeywardena.",
        "It is reported that the reason for this could be that the President has not yet reached his destination. The President had informed the Speaker that he would forward the letter of resignation before 12.00 midnight yesterday."
      ],
